    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黏糊糊快跑！》是一款适合所有玩家的轻松上手游戏！简单易学却难以精通！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受《耀西岛》《星之卡比》等家庭向平台游戏启发，本作将魅力与挑战完美融合，凭借直观操作和难度递增的关卡，不断给玩家带来惊喜并考验技巧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/7ee22f81cbfce7c8579d4fb9137898fe.gif?t=1767745878\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/7ee22f81cbfce7c8579d4fb9137898fe.poster.avif?t=1767745878\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在五个独特世界中，穿越精心手绘的关卡，一路弹跳前行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >避免冲突，不战而胜！敌人（大多！）无害，而你这个小黏糊糊同样无伤大雅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的软绵绵正是最强武器！弹跳至敌人身上、钻进敌人体内、跃过敌人头顶，不断攀登新高度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在BOSS战中生存下来——你并非攻击目标！别卷入善恶终极对决的漩涡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/0aff75438e8683b67a14f045e12e2008.poster.avif?t=1767745878\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/0aff75438e8683b67a14f045e12e2008.webm?t=1767745878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/0aff75438e8683b67a14f045e12e2008.mp4?t=1767745878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快跑吧，黏糊糊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/484ff24ee28b91324d92cdb2d664a050.poster.avif?t=1767745878\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/484ff24ee28b91324d92cdb2d664a050.webm?t=1767745878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215230/extras/484ff24ee28b91324d92cdb2d664a050.mp4?t=1767745878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
